Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把他送到了你也要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和打开真理之门的感觉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不用管这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠没法承受这个重量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去担心大爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯兵 来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁是医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有会用炼金术的医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 这里有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想怎么用就怎么用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是炼金术师大国亚美斯多利斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使得到长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也救不了一个臣子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让布拉德雷受了致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有让胡白白牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却不能为你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最后的弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也没子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自用枪应战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果觉得我有恩于你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能接受我一个请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家女王大人下令之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我保护它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我的计划还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳去保护这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你答应了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会 遵守盟约
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击射击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有家人 有恋人的人都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没兴趣和女人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该说是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更可靠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 请振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能安心地去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将马上就会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉要在中央都市活跃才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央都市这满是黑烟的天空不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到比布里克斯的山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更高一点的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕卡尼亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的光是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何发表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么样了 军队司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都的广播没有后续报导吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的广播台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在重复播报禁止外出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广播说了不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃去塔芭莎家吧 艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里也能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妈妈一起看日食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士 你知道是怎么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从艾尔利克兄弟那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行人体炼成的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑色的手拉进真理之门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理之门是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下 本部没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么关于伊兹米的情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫正门的帕卡尼亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和部下数名一同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和金格·布拉德雷的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉和清国的人协力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使布拉德雷受了致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他推到了护城河里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个金格·布拉德雷怎么会这么简单地死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是超越人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正门怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被守着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫古利德的人造人在协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松打倒了正门的中央兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人怎么会反抗那位大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕卡尼亚大尉笑着走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他笑着走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格先生 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须要找到你的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么师傅会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想要问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就被带到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连阿尔也拉来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（阿尔 振作点）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（能听见吗 阿尔）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人柱都被集中在一起了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还少一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余一个现在正在做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个怪物是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连阿尔冯斯也被抓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连伊兹米小姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么没用的样子 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我安分点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你体内的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会我慢慢来吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个黑黑的家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人造人称为父亲大人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是那个胡须混蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我破坏了他的皮袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说多余的话 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎到来 各位人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 上面的家伙们真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了今天 连5个人柱都弄不齐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些被长生不老钓上来的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会干活是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你主动协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能否进行人体炼成来帮我打开门呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你很要好的…叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们来帮你准备一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人柱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开门的人能成为人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以艾尔利克兄弟被选中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从他们那里听说人体炼成不可能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有哪个笨蛋明知道会失败还去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你只要打开门然后回来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会进行人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 来打开门吧 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听见吗 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快进行人体炼成 成为第5个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话 这个女人的性命就保不住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人死了的话你会炼成她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…接受了不能死的命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样就能得到不死之身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就不会那么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古君 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最重要的女人快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不管就会失血过多而死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是会使用炼金术的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还拿着贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的话 一定能拯救这个女人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 在你决定之前死掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是我也没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要…进行人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会做的吧 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有一时好转
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是转瞬即逝的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你所站立之处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是迷窟之入口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第59话 失去了的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终结的时刻就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:07.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:02.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:41.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:46.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:12.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:39.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:46.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:52.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
